Notes

1.

For dual- or quad-DIMM configurations, you must use a pair of identical DDR4 modules.

2.

For dual-DIMM configuration, you must use a pair of identical DDR3L modules.

3.

The system is shipped without HDD.

For the HDD compatibility list, please visit https://www.qnap.com/compatibility/

4.

The following are not hot-swappable: M.2 SSDs, SSD cache drives, SSDs using PCIe expansion slots.

5.

The M.2 SSD is not included as standard.

M.2 SSD operations can easily generate excessive heat. It is recommended to install a heatsink (from QNAP or a third-party provider) on the M.2 SSD.

6.

Expandable with an optional PCIe adapter

7.

PCIe bandwidth limitations will restrict the NAS 10GbE performance.

8.

You cannot use the speakers and the line-out jack simultaneously.

9.

Tested with drives fully populated.

10.

Tested fully populated with 2TB hard drives.
